hopobject.body: Best Site Good Work www.bankmed.com.lb Marbury, 36, has played for the CBA since 2010, and is said to be contemplating a future in coaching with the Ducks. He's so beloved in the capital city that after he led Beijing to the team's first championship two years ago, the team erected a statue of him that sits outside the team's stadium, a monument to second-chances if ever there was one. Marbury's cousin, Sebastian Telfair, has also reportedly signed to play in the CBA this season for Tianjin with an eye toward returning to the NBA early next year.
